            <h1 class="font-size-2 text-bahama-blue font-weight-bold">About CICT</h1>
            <p class="font-size-1 text-secondary">The Conference on Information and Communication Technology (CICT) is
                the annual
                flagship conference jointly organized by the five Ministry of Human Resources Development (MHRD)-funded
                Indian Institutes of Information Technology (IIITs) namely, Atal Bihari Vajpayee Indian Institute of
                Information Technology and Management (ABV-IIITM) Gwalior, IIIT Allahabad, PDPM - Indian Institute of
                Information Technology Design and Manufacturing (IIITDM) Jabalpur, IIITDM Kancheepuram and IIITDM
                Kurnool. CICT aims to provide a forum for researchers, industry professionals, and academicians to
                present and exchange their ideas in latest technological advancements and innovations in the field of
                Information and Communication Technology.</p>
        </div>
